      "file_path": "ansible/roles/rancher/tasks/rancher_agent.yml",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 10,
      "message": "I decided to remove this line.\nReason: the only thing it does is ensuring container being removed on stop, however we don't actually do it anywhere else explicitly, so I don't see it causing problems.\nNamely rancher server itself is not running with --rm. why this one should?\nOf course what caused this line to be removed was the fact that python-docker in the version shipped in rhel does not support auto_remove. It is easier to remove the line if it is not really needed, than\nto upgrade python-docker to newer version, especially that this updating code was removed.",
